race.comment: REVENGEANCE (1) showed a ton of grit on debut when covering ground in the run for a solid third over 1000m in the G3 Breeders' Plate at Randwick. Since fitted with a 742m tick-over trial placing and looks ready to go on with it now from the right barrier. THRILL HUNTER (11) specked late in betting at the big odds on debut, when she showed good early toe to hold off all challengers for a surprise win over 1000m at Randwick in the Kirkham. Can prove that win was no fluke from the low draw. ARTEMEX (5) Exceed And Excel colt from Artemis Rose on debut for the Maher yard. Had plenty up the sleeve when a recent Warwick Farm trial winner over 818m. Tongue-tie goes on and gets his chance with Rawiller aboard. THE NEXT EPISODE (8) another from the Maher yard on debut. Well bred colt by Snitzel from the stakes-winning mare Humma Humma. Looks ready to go after his slick trial win over 900m at Rosehill. DEFENSEMEN (2) slowly into stride on debut when a tough third in the Kirkham. Respect.
